
PetoMatsi
---

1.Introduction

PetoMatsi is simple "do-your-own-nibbles" - toolkit made
with javascript and html5. It might not be too useful
but atleast it's a little bit fun and it was fun to make :)

2. Tutorial

Check example petomatsi.htm to get started.
All the parameterized values are shown in
the example. You can play with the parameters
and see the results with yourself

3. Parameters

levels : Array of Arrays of numbers 1 and 0 where 
         1 defines the wall and 0 empty space.
         NOTE! Required

maxScore : numbers of 'noms' per level. default is 9

blockSize : size of the game element block. default is 10

speed : game speed in ms. default is 50

colors : object of color values for different game elements.
         game elements are (name, default value) ->
                  border : "red",
                  empty : "blue"
                  mato : "yellow",
                  nom : "white"




